 · 20 sty 2018
I visited #Afrin in Aug 2015. Back then already enclave, difficult to enter. Except frontlines, Afrin very quiet, no war damage. Daily life normal. Beautiful nature. Many Kurdish &Arab refugees fled to Afrin 2 enjoy peace. Clearly this now changing. Here some pics I took in 2015.
