When I visited #Afrin-enclave in 2015, YPG already digging trenches &tunnels to be prepared for this day. 

Tunnels r on front with Nusra/AlQaeda (south), rebels (east) &Turkey (north, west). 

So it won't be a walkover, but not clear to me how Kurds can deal with aerial bombing.
